thread.title_full: Extra Space Storage reviewed by Sandra LaMartz

author: Sandra LaMartz
title: Sandra LaMartz
text: I'm relocating, and was shopping for a storage wasn't feeling well that day, happen to look up to see CubeSmart Storage, I met this amazing person name Bobby that made shopping for a storage a fun adventure I didn't know exactly what I was looking for,Bobby help me make the right choice he was very helpful and pleasant storage nice & roomy, very clean I'm very satisfied with my choice, thank you Bobby see you soon. S.LaMartz
